data.description: Sellers are motivated - bring all offers! Beautiful, large 3 bedroom, 2 bath on 1.08 acre parcel that backs up to 20 acre woodlands in north Floral City.  2018 Live Oak Manufactured Home with all the whistles and bells.  Large kitchen with eat in nook and center island.  Laminate flooring throughout, huge master walk in closet, inside laundry room/mud room.  Accessory buildings, fully fenced!  This home is priced to sell , spacious enough for a family, perfect if you like privacy in the backyard.  Paved road in a nice neighborhood. Horses are not allowed in this zoning areas for <2 acre parcels, so NO horses.
